title: Bug 109350 - Output parameter not displaying in data set dialog
OB: While on the query result page, no data is returned. The actual result is that the output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: Expect the output parameter to be visible in the edit data set dialog when viewing query results.
SR:
1. Open the application and navigate to the query result page. 
2. Observe that no data is returned. 
3. Click on the 'Edit Data Set' option. 
4. Verify if the output parameter is displayed in the edit data set dialog.
